Package org.sopra.api.model.producer

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BioGasFiredPowerPlant
    A power plant that is fired by biogas (extracted from corn or more disgusting sources).
    CoalFiredPowerPlant
    A power plant fired by coal.
    ControllableProducer
    Controllable producers are producers that have an adjustable energy consumption.
    GasFiredPowerPlant
    A power plant fired by natural gas.
    HydroPowerPlant
    A power plant that uses a river or a dam to generate power by a turbine.
    NuclearPowerPlant
    A nuclear power plant.
    Producer
    Interface for energy nodes that produce energy, for example power plants.
    SolarPowerPlant
    A power plant consisting of solar cells.
    WindPowerPlant
    A power plant generating energy from wind.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ProducerType
    An enumeration to simplify the determination the type of a consumers: biogas-fired power plant coal-fired power plant gas-fired power plant hydro power plant nuclear power plant solar power plant wind power plant
